<span STYLE="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacsystemFont,">
路边的华表</SPAN><br />
<a HREF="http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/001wKg5zzy7xBLvNg0xa9" TARGET="_blank"><img src="http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src ="http://s10.sinaimg.cn/mw690/001wKg5zzy7xBLvNg0xa9&amp;690" NAME="image_operate_3561570452992839"  ALT="京城闹市寻幽（85）：探访怡贤亲王允祥墓"  TITLE="京城闹市寻幽（85）：探访怡贤亲王允祥墓" /></A><br />
<span STYLE="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacsystemFont,">
华表的柱头，没有神兽</SPAN><br />
